    • Field Summary

      Fields 
      Modifier and Type Field and Description
      (package private) short edgeBitmap
      The edge bitmap which specifies if there is an incoming/outgoing edge of each type 2 bits per edge type(1 for incoming, 1 for outgoing) for a total of 8 types = 16 bits = short
      (package private) short[] edgeNums
      array holding the number of edges incident with the vertex of a given type The array length will be 8, one for each type

      The vertex id

      The type of the vertex.
